msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Vectrex controller"
msgstr "Ovladač Vectrex"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Vectrex was released in 1982 by General Consumer Electronics (later purchased by Milton Bradley). The console featured a built-in monochrome monitor capable of displaying vector graphics."
msgstr "Vectrex vydala v roce 1982 společnost General Consumer Electronics (později koupená společností Milton Bradley). Konzole měla vestavěný monochromatický monitor schopný zobrazovat vektorovou grafiku."

